## Deployment Architecture

### Vercel Deployment

```
Local Development
  │
  ├─→ git push origin main
  │
  └─→ Vercel CI/CD
      ├── Install Dependencies
      ├── Build Command: npm run build
      ├── Output Dir: dist/
      │
      ├─→ Vercel Edge Network
      │   ├── Global CDN
      │   ├── Web Analytics
